---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Maprofile | 馬副的研究空間">
  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center overflow-hidden py-16 px-6">
    
    <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-blue-600/10 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-blob"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-40 -right-20 w-[350px] h-[350px] bg-emerald-600/10 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-blob [animation-delay:2s]"></div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative w-full text-center">
      
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 mb-6 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-blue-400 uppercase bg-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full">
        學術與科技研究個人檔案
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-black text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        歡迎來到 <span class="text-gradient">馬副(測試版)</span> 的研究空間
      </h1>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto text-sm mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        專注於科學計算與社會實踐，在數據與永續發展之間尋找跨學科的交集。
      </p>

      <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-16 text-left">
        
        <div class="group relative p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 hover:border-blue-500/50 hover:bg-blue-500/[0.05] transition-all duration-500 cursor-help">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
            <span class="text-[10px] text-blue-400 font-black tracking-widest uppercase">Gauss's Law</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono">01</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">高斯定律</h3>
          <div class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left">
            ∇ · E = ρ / ε₀
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-400 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-3">
            描述電荷如何產生電場。電場線從正電荷出發，終止於負電荷。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 hover:border-green-500/50 hover:bg-green-500/[0.05] transition-all duration-500 cursor-help">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
            <span class="text-[10px] text-green-400 font-black tracking-widest uppercase">Gauss's Law for Magnetism</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono">02</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">高斯磁定律</h3>
          <div class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left">
            ∇ · B = 0
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-400 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-3">
            說明自然界中不存在磁單極（磁鐵一定有南北極）。磁場線永遠是封閉迴圈。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 hover:border-yellow-500/50 hover:bg-yellow-500/[0.05] transition-all duration-500 cursor-help">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
            <span class="text-[10px] text-yellow-400 font-black tracking-widest uppercase">Faraday's Law</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono">03</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">法拉第感應定律</h3>
          <div class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left">
            ∇ × E = − ∂B / ∂t
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-400 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-3">
            描述變化的磁場如何產生感應電場。這是發電機運作的核心原理。
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="group relative p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/10 hover:border-purple-500/50 hover:bg-purple-500/[0.05] transition-all duration-500 cursor-help">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
            <span class="text-[10px] text-purple-400 font-black tracking-widest uppercase">Ampère-Maxwell Law</span>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 font-mono">04</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">安培-馬克士威定律</h3>
          <div class="text-xl font-serif text-slate-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-500 origin-left">
            ∇ × B = μ₀(J + ε₀ ∂E / ∂t)
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 text-xs text-slate-400 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-3">
            描述電流與變化的電場如何產生磁場。這解釋了電磁波如何在真空傳播。
          </div>
        </div>

      </section>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/projects" class="group px-8 py-3 bg-white text-slate-900 font-bold rounded-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          探索研究成果
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/posts" class="px-8 py-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all backdrop-blur-sm">
          閱讀日誌
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>